N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 215.1 - Application

State Regulations

The policy set forth in this Part shall apply
to all courts of the Unified Court System except those that already have a
requirement for the filing of court papers on recycled paper. Notes
